** {{mes|You need 25 stone rocks to build this stage of the bridge. Mine some nearby.}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player has no hammer:}}
** {{mes|You need a hammer to be able to build the bridge.}}
** {{tact|end}}
