** {{tbox|You have successfully started construction on the bridge.}}
** {{tact|end}}

====Completing the second stage====
* {{tcond|If the player has at least 25 stones and a hammer:}}
** {{tbox|You have successfully continued construction of the bridge.}}
** {{tact|end}}

====Completing the bridge====
* {{tcond|If the player has at least 25 stones and a hammer:}}
